title: The Origin of Galactus
description:
The Origin Of Galactus
Marvel Comics
February 1996
Featuring: Galactus, Reed Richards/Mr. Fantastic, Johnny Storm/The Human Torch, Ben Grimm/The Thing, Sue Storm/Invisible Girl.
Written by Stan Lee, Mark Gruenwald.
Penciler Jack Kirby, John Byrne.
Inker George Klein, Terry Austin.
Letterer Art Simek, John Morelli.
Colorist Andy Yanchus.
One-Shot


Reprints of The Fantastic Four issues # 48-50.
